Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
reset_pulse_clock_max_width(25.10)          reset_pulse_clock_max_width(25.10)

Name
       reset_pulse_clock_max_width

Syntax
       reset_pulse_clock_max_width

       <object_list>

       [-transitive_fanout]

       Resets  the  maximum  pulse clock width constraint specified (using the
       set_pulse_clock_max_width command) on the pulse generator cells,  pulse
       generator library cells, clocks, and/or current design.

Parameters
       <object_list>
              Specifies  a list of objects - pulse generator cells, pulse gen-
              erator library cells, clocks, or current design - for which  the
              maximum pulse clock width is to be reset.

       [-transitive_fanout]
              Specifies the pulse width value for transitive fanout.

Related Information
              * set_pulse_clock_max_width

